title: Lowest Maternal Mortality Ratio
description: In 2016, Czechia reported a maternal mortality ratio of just 1 per 100,000 live births, one of the lowest globally, indicating excellent maternal healthcare.

title: High Dependence on Manufactured Imports
description: By 2024, 83.68% of Czechia's merchandise imports consisted of manufactured goods, highlighting a significant reliance on foreign manufactured products.
